### 관리자 게시판 API 테스트

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@admin.com",
  "password": "admin12!!@"
}

> {% client.global.set("adminToken", response.body.data.token) %}

### 새 게시판 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/board
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "테스트 게시판",
  "categoryId": 2
}

### ID로 게시판 조회 (Deprecated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/board/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 모든 게시판 조회 (Deprecated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/board
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 게시판 수정
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/board
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "수정된 테스트 게시판",
  "permission": "ALL",
  "isMainExposed": true
}

### 게시판 삭제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/board/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
